item.dc:creator: @Project_Evolution Project Evolution
item.description:
@Project_Evolution wrote:

GZipper Here

Make a new folder, and in it put the attachment and make a new bat file. Dont forget to extract what’s contained in this rar package.

In the bat file put:

gzip *.dat

Then simply run the bat file when you have a .dat file in the folder
